    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE PROPHECY IS COMING!</h2><br>An invitation to research ancient menhirs sends you to Brittany to find these magnificent standing stones...<br>But you quickly discover there is far more at stake than groundbreaking research. <br>...there is a prophecy...<br>One that foretells chaos and evil being unleashed upon the world on the night when a comet hides behind the moon and turns the sky purple.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TONIGHT IS THAT NIGHT!</h2><br>Can you race against the clock to save not only yourself but the fate of two worlds?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467490/extras/f48bad1787b6398ff6891f3ee1f4783e.avif?t=1550078296\" width=600 height=396 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover secrets hidden in a sleepy town in Brittany, France.<br></li><li>Travel between worlds to the mythical land of Avalon.<br></li><li> Find out the truth about an ancient druidic prophecy and stop it before it's too late.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRAVEN The Purple Moon Prophecy IN FIGURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>38 locations in the game (counting things like full screen laptop view as separate location)<br></li><li>35 locations in the game (counting only separate physical places as locations)<br></li><li>22 mini-games<br></li><li>9 characters<br></li><li>19 achievements (if anything changed)<br></li><li>29 cutscenes (14 minutes of full screen video)<br></li><li>10 hidden object scenes, each of them in two variants<br></li><li>7 chapters</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/467490/extras/9c82b7796ac4313127f17ea07480533a.avif?t=1550078296\" width=600 height=396 /></span>",
